{"tid":457776,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"面試考沖柯華田？聖保羅校長否認：要自然地傾偈","createTime":"2017-11-04T08:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T08:21:48.000Z","uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c043ecf882a4496bd1080941b04c96b9d54bb9","tid":457776,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T08:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171104/large/1509778413_d263.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171104%2Flarge%2F1509778413_d263.png&h=d8ba7025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖保羅書院校長源廸恩強調自然對答最好，學生背誦對答，會影響面試表現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171104/57417068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171104%2F57417068&d=R%2F%2BmfF0kYNTsCQBSFggLuVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=e8d4a0cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171104%2F57417068&h=2d90f09f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171104/57417068</a><br />\n<br />\n傳統直資名校聖保羅書院今日舉辦中一簡介會，校方指有1,600至1,700人參與，坐滿禮堂及其他課室，為歷來人數最多。校長源廸恩表示，去年有約千人報名，共面試550至560人，今年面試名額約600個，最終取錄約100人，與去年相若，有80個名額保另預留10個「叩門」名額。<br />\n<br />\n源廸恩指，學校重視中英語文能力，但面試不會問學生能力範圍以外的問題，亦不會問時事題，問題會很生活化，「煮蝦、沖柯華田不是生活化」，例如會讓學生觀看圖畫，「傾下偈」，題目如中秋節、聖誕節，確保學生可以發揮和對答。<br />\n<br />\n對於不少學生參加面試班，他指，學生背誦自我介紹和對答，「會知道佢哋背緊嘢」，會對面試表現有影響，但老師很有經驗，會再以其他方法問，目的測試學生的應對能力，強調自然對答最好，「有多啲自己嘢，唔使講讀幾年班、有幾多家庭成員、平時玩咩，可以講下自己鍾意咩、自豪參加咩，但冇標準，要自然地傾偈。」<br />\n<br />\n學生收生比例以考試成績佔60%，面試佔30%，課外活動佔10%。學校今日起接受報名，網上申請及書面申請的截止日期分別為下月21日及22日，預計明年1月底會通知考生面試，3月3日進行面試，3月底公佈面試結果。學費為每年40,400元。<br />\n<br />\n面試分中文及英文部分，英文只設個人面試，以1對2兩位老師對答，廣東話除設個人面試，需要1對2位老師對答，亦有5至6名學生小組討論環節。<br />\n<br />\n另外，學校今年首設一班GCE班，以數理科目為主，將於2020年考試，屆時會再作檢討，但最多只會加至兩班。<br />\n<br />\n許先生帶同小五兒子提早一年到場了解，相信明年會報讀，而兒子一般語文能力不俗，亦有參與劍擊和製作機械人課外活動，不用特別催谷。陳生陳太今日參加第二場簡介會，陳先生指由於兒子就讀中文小學，將為兒子加強英文，將報讀一至兩間學校。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171104/large/1509778128_da80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171104%2Flarge%2F1509778128_da80.jpg&h=1966bdf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳太參加第二場簡介會，指由於兒子就讀中文小學，將為兒子加強英文。（周智堅攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171104/large/1509778125_855a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171104%2Flarge%2F1509778125_855a.jpg&h=f4d2a052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許先生帶同小五兒子提早一年到場了解，相信明年會報讀。（周智堅攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171104/large/1509778579_5efb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171104%2Flarge%2F1509778579_5efb.jpg&h=d767a3b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171104/large/1509778628_521a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171104%2Flarge%2F1509778628_521a.jpg&h=5c5bc844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171104/large/1509778631_f217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171104%2Flarge%2F1509778631_f217.jpg&h=34d462be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171104/large/1509778663_4162.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171104%2Flarge%2F1509778663_4162.jpg&h=374f05d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171104/large/1509778666_702c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171104%2Flarge%2F1509778666_702c.jpg&h=982019ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f279e4c537ef7f9afa4a7d7ac7152ba1e2a11e09","tid":457776,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T08:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/161724_304d544442bec7059e2eded19ec6de25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F161724_304d544442bec7059e2eded19ec6de25.jpg&h=bda3f441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位家長好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e4d231c84298c07c69c558970fe57cbfdf6796","tid":457776,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T08:21:48.000Z","msg":"邊度靚仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}